snippet.title: 🚨 Daily life Safety with AMBER  | EP 01 - 04 | Robocar POLI | Kids animation
snippet.description:
In Brooms Town, where the Robocar Poli rescue headquarter is located, Peter, the head of the accident lane, lives with his father, his mother, his sister Lucie and his doggy buddy.

Peter, along with his best friend Johnny, A prim-looking Cindy, and the frightened schoolboy Charles, rushes around town for fun and exciting adventures. However, there’s always a risk of safety accidents behind the pleasant days of children. Our safety fairy, “Amber!", Protects precious lives against emergency situations and disasters caused by mistakes and carelessness at home, school, and playground.

After the rescue is completed, AMBER provides easy and systematic explanations tailored to the child's eye level and safety rules to prevent accidents. Thanks to the friendly and smart Amber and the rescue team, Brooms Town is lively and peaceful today!
